classes.name: swaplist
classes.description: Defines the style for the base swaplist component.

classes.name: swaplist__content
classes.description:
Provides the style for the main content of the swaplist, which includes the two lists
and their filters, but not the shared filter.

classes.name: swaplist__side
classes.description:
Provides the style for one side of the swaplist. A side includes the filter, 
header labels and buttons, and the list itself.

classes.name: swaplist__list-divider
classes.description: Provides the style for the divider between the two lists of the swaplist.
